    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We calculated the impact of early social distancing on the COVID-19 transmission in the S\u00e3o Paulo metropolitan area and forecasted the ICU beds needed to cope the epidemic demand by using an age-stratified SEIR model. Within 60 days, these measures would avoid 89,133 deaths.</jats:p>",
